---
title: "Hi there, I'm Emily. A chocolate sculptress from Vermont."
description: "Some say I'm obsessed with chocolate. I take that as a compliment. Making [creations](/sculptures/) out of something so universally loved is fun and rewarding. Especially the look on people's faces when they realize what I've built is completely edible."
navtitle: Home
permalink: index.html
---
{% extends "layouts/base.njk" %}

{% block content %}
<header class="u-linear c-header">
    <h1 class="u-font-size-xl">{{ title }}</h1>
    {{ description | markdownify | safe }}
</header>

<section class="intro u-linear">
    <h2>All Roads Lead to Chocolate</h2>
    <div class="c-avatar" style="--aspect-ratio: 1/1;">
      <img src="/assets/img/home-collage.jpg" alt="A collage of Emily on a TV set and sculpting chocolate">
    </div>
    <p>The <a href="/about/" title="Becoming a Chocolate Sculptress">path to becoming a chocolate sculptress</a> has been long and winding, but well worth the journey. Along the way I've had the honor of studying with great chocolate artists while working for <a href="http://www.lakechamplainchocolates.com">Lake Champlain Chocolates</a>.</p>
    {% Quote {
        text: "&ldquo;There is nothing better than a friend, unless it is a friend with chocolate.&rdquo; &#8211; Linda Grayson",
        size: "u-font-size-xl"
    } %}
    <p>Chocolate is a wonderful, finicky, and delicious medium to sculpt with. This ever-changing and challenging medium continues to inspire me. Above all else I hope it brings a smile to your face.</p>
</section>

<section class="u-linear">
    <h2>Featured Sculptures</h2>
    <div class="o-grid" style="--min-column: 250px;">
    {%- for sculpture in collections.sculptures | favorites(3) %}
      <article class="c-card" id="product-1">
        <div style="--aspect-ratio: 7/5;"><img src="/assets/sculptures/{{ sculpture.fileSlug }}/thumbnail.jpg" alt="Photo of {{ sculpture.data.title }}" loading="lazy"></div>
        <h3 class="c-card__heading"><a href="{{ sculpture.url }}">{{ sculpture.data.title }}<svg aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path><path fill="currentcolor" d="M12 4l-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H4v2h12.17l-5.58 5.59L12 20l8-8z"></path></svg></a></h3>
      </article>
    {%- endfor %}
    </div>
    <div class="u-center u-margin-top-3">{% Link '/sculptures', 'All sculptures' %}</div>
</section>

<section class="u-linear">
    <h2>In the Press</h2>
    {% Figure {
        breakout: false,
        ratio: 20/3.7,
        src: '/assets/img/press-seen-on.jpg',
        alt: title + ' graphics'
    } %}
    <div class="u-center u-margin-top-3">{% Link '/press', 'All press' %}</div>
</section>

<section class="u-linear">
    <h2>Recent Posts</h2>
    <ul class="c-listing">
    {% for post in collections.posts | take(5) %}
    <li class="c-listing__item">
        <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
    </li>
    {% endfor %}
    </ul>
    <div class="u-center u-margin-top-3">{% Link '/journal', 'Read my chocolate journal' %}</div>
</section>
{% endblock %}